msgid "Welcome"
msgstr "Selamat Datang"

msgid ""
"This is the installation wizard. If you are new to using this theme, don't "
"worry! It will help you to set up or do the installation in just a few easy "
"steps."
msgstr ""
"Ini adalah wizard instalasi. Jika Anda baru menggunakan tema ini, jangan "
"khawatir! Ini akan membantu anda untuk menyiapkan atau melakukan instalasi "
"dengan hanya beberapa langkah mudah."

msgid "Start Installing Now"
msgstr "Mulai Instal Sekarang"

msgid "Skip installation Wizard"
msgstr "Lewati Wizard Instalasi"

msgid "Theme Activation"
msgstr "Aktivasi Tema"

msgid ""
"First, you need to activate the theme by entering the license key below. If "
"you don't have it, please log in to the member area or my account on the "
"garudatheme website."
msgstr ""
"Pertama, Anda perlu melakukan aktivasi tema dengan memasukkan kunci lisensi "
"dibawah. Jika tidak memilikinya, silahkan masuk ke member area atau akun "
"saya di website garudatheme."

msgid "Successfully activated"
msgstr "Berhasil diaktivasi"

msgid "Next"
msgstr "Selanjutnya"

msgid "Previous"
msgstr "Sebelumnya"

msgid "Install Plugins"
msgstr "Instal Plugin"

msgid "For the theme to work, please install the required plugins."
msgstr "Agar tema dapat berjalan, silahkan instal plugin yang dibutuhkan."

msgid "Type"
msgstr "Tipe"

msgid "Required"
msgstr "Dibutuhkan"

msgid "Optional"
msgstr "Opsional"

msgid "Already active"
msgstr "Sudah aktif"

msgid "Not active"
msgstr "Belum aktif"

msgid ""
"To install the required plugins, please select the Appearance menu then "
"click %s."
msgstr ""
"Untuk menginstal plugin yang dibutuhkan, silahkan pilih menu Tampilan "
"kemudian klik %s."

msgid "Completed"
msgstr "Selesai"

msgid ""
"At this point, the theme has been successfully installed. Next, you can "
"proceed to the next step as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Sampai disini tema sudah berhasil diinstal. Selanjutnya silahkan lanjut "
"ketahap berikutnya dengan mengikuti perintah berikut:"

msgid "Import Demo Content"
msgstr "Import Konten Demo"

msgid "Customize Display"
msgstr "Sesuaikan Tampilan"

msgid "Manage Posts"
msgstr "Kelola Postingan"

msgid ""
"Import the content on the demo web, and customize the theme automatically "
"with just a few clicks using the import demo data tool of the one click demo "
"import plugin."
msgstr ""
"Import konten pada web demo, dan sesuaikan tampilan hanya dengan beberapa "
"klik menggunakan alat import demo data dari plugin one click demo import."

msgid ""
"Customize the appearance such as colors, fonts, sections, and many more in "
"the theme options."
msgstr ""
"Sesuaikan tampilan seperti warna, font, section, dan masih banyak lagi "
"lainnya pada pengaturan tema."

msgid ""
"Manage posts by creating, deleting, or editing posts and pages on your "
"website."
msgstr ""
"Kelola postingan dengan membuat, menghapus, atau mengedit postingan dan "
"halaman pada website Anda."

msgid "Exit"
msgstr "Keluar"

msgid ""
"Enter the license key, dont have one yet? get it <a href=\"%s\" target="
"\"_blank\">here</a>."
msgstr ""
"Masukkan kunci lisensi, tidak punya? dapatkan <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank"
"\">disini</a>."

msgid ""
"This site uses a theme that has not been activated, if you are an admin, "
"please activate it %shere%s."
msgstr ""
"Website ini menggunakan tema yang belum diaktivasi, jika Anda admin, silakan "
"aktivasi %sdisini%s."

msgid "All Google Fonts sorted alphabetically"
msgstr "Semua Font Google diurutkan berdasarkan abjad"

msgid "Select weight for"
msgstr "Pilih ketebalan untuk"

msgid "Select weight & style for regular text"
msgstr "Pilih ketebalan & gaya untuk teks biasa"

msgid "bold text"
msgstr "teks bold"

msgid "italic text"
msgstr "teks miring"
